<Name type="Text" ref="y">Similar to Treepad</Name>
<Text type="Text" lines="20">This file provides a single long text field for each node.
This is similar to how the Treepad program on windows is usually used.</Text>
</PLAIN_TEXT>
<PLAIN_TEXT item="y">
<Name ref="y">Plain text field</Name>
<Text>Text fields can be set to plain text, so all line breaks and other white space are preserved.

You can also use characters like &lt;, &gt; and &amp; without escaping them.</Text>
</PLAIN_TEXT>
