<Name type="Text" ref="y">HTML text field</Name>
<Text type="Text" html="y" lines="20">An HTML field allows tags like &lt;i&gt;itallics&lt;/&gt; to be used.

It does not preserve white space.

Characters like &amp;lt;, &amp;gt;, and &amp;amp; must be escaped.</Text>
